#: app/templates/www/features.html:16
msgid ""
"Not a generic CRM. Built for manufacturing — drawings, revisions, "
"deadlines, customer material on stock."
msgstr ""
"Ne obecné CRM. Postavené pro výrobu — výkresy, revize, termíny, materiál "
